ARCHITECT Homocysteine Reagent Kit, 100 Tests
 Microparticles : 1 or 4 Bottle(s) (6.5 mL each) Anti-S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine coated microparticles in BIS-TRIS buffer with surfactants.

 Conjugate : 1 or 4 Bottle(s) (5.7 mL each) S-adenosyl-L-cysteine (SAC) acridinium-labeled conjugate in citrate buffer with surfactants.

 Enzyme : 1 or 4 Bottle(s) (8.6 mL each) Recombinant S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine hydrolase (SAHHase) in 4-(2-hydroxyethyl) piperazine-1-propane sulfonic acid (EPPS) buffer.

 Reductant : 1 or 4 Bottle(s) (21.5 mL each) Dithiothreitol (DTT) in citrate buffer.


ARCHITECT Homocysteine Calibrators
6 Bottles (3.6 mL each) of ARCHITECT Homocysteine Calibrators. Calibrators A-F contain phosphate buffer. Calibrators B-F also contain gravimetrically prepared S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine. The calibrators(A-F) yield the following concentrations(µmol/L):0.0, 2.5, 5.0, 10.0, 20.0 and 50.0 .
